Class ConnectionMap<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.treetank.service.xml.diff.algorithm.fmes.ConnectionMap<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - 

    public final class ConnectionMap<T>
extends Object
    Stores whether two objects have a (unidirectional) connection. /!\ The identities of the objects are used, not equals()!
